ence Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132280339,imgsize-911092.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Temperatures set to peak at 36C during UK heatwave, health warnings issued]]></title><description><![CDATA[The United Kingdom faces its third heatwave of 2026 with temperatures soaring. Health authorities have issued alerts as hospitals experience sustained pressure from the heat. Vulnerable communities and older people are at increased risk of illness and death. People are advised to drink water and stay cool during the hottest hours. This extreme weather aligns with broader climate change patterns affecting Europe.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/temperatures-set-to-peak-at-36c-during-uk-heatwave-health-warnings-issued/articleshow/132280612.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/temperatures-set-to-peak-at-36c-during-uk-heatwave-health-warnings-issued/articleshow/132280612.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-09T13:41:58+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132281140,imgsize-126923.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Japanese Soldier’s Jungle Surrender: Onoda obeys orders for 29 years; his pardon ignites debate]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132280169.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-japanese-soldier-stayed-hidden-in-a-philippine-jungle-for-29-years-because-he-believed-world-war-ii-never-ended/articleshow/132280169.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/a-japanese-soldier-stayed-hidden-in-a-philippine-jungle-for-29-years-because-he-believed-world-war-ii-never-ended/articlesho